snippet.title: Sands of Time - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
By Debuglog & Woon
Patch Download Link (For OoT 1.0 USA .z64 rom, credit document included):
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/19YAUqU4EMfch8lAz2LQZxuTrmPxitaUr?usp=sharing
You can apply the patch here:
https://www.marcrobledo.com/RomPatcher.js/

It was only tested on the following emulators:
Project64 3.0 with GlideN64 graphics plgin.
RetroArch with MupenPlus-Next core.
It's beatable on real hardware according to feedback
(WARNING: You'll experience lots of laggs in several optional areas on real hardware)
Parallel graphics plugin can theoretically run, expecting unintended graphics glitch.

Join z64Modding server for giving your feedback & reporting bug.
https://discord.gg/ubuG9BK8BZ
If you get crash & graphics glitches on emulators outside of the ones mentioned above, I can't help you.
